metadata.name: Earth healing
metadata.description: All human souls are connected to the united spiritual consciousness, energy and soul of the planet earth. Therefore, the more people in the world concern about their soul purification and  getting in touch with their spiritual side, the more planet earth get purified and the less evil exists in the world. There is strength in unity; individually we, people, are drops but together we are an ocean. We should get united to purify our souls all together and spread energy of love for healing and purifying the earth from evil, and wickedness.
